  <name>Clash GNOME</name>
  <summary>Modern GNOME frontend for the mihomo (Clash Meta) proxy</summary>
  <description>
    <p>Clash GNOME is a native GTK4 + libadwaita GUI for the mihomo (Clash Meta) proxy core. It provides:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Subscription management with quota tracking</li>
      <li>Proxy group selection and latency testing</li>
      <li>Rule inspection and connection monitoring</li>
      <li>TUN mode with system stack support</li>
      <li>Adaptive light/dark theming</li>
      <li>Autostart integration and background hidden mode</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
